content.rendered:
Directed by Donna Brockopp. Katya Bowser.

Written by Elise Allen. Elise Allen. Sindy Boveda-Spackman. Gus Constantellis. Dena Diamond. Isabel Galupo. Jack Monaco. Savannah Guthrie. Sara Karimipour. Jeannette Lara. Jacquie Menville. Charity L. Miller. Allison Oppenheim.

Cast Trinity Jo-Li Bliss (Rita Raspberry). Dana Heath (Kira Kiwi). Luna Bella Zamora (Penny Pineapple). Madison Calderon (Bea Blueberry). Rita Moreno (Bussyboots). Andrew Rannells (King Barton). Jenna Ushkowitz (Queen Ryung). Ian Loh (Joon). Tan France (Sir Benedict). Micaiah Chen (Ara). Eric Bauza (Seung). Ciera Payton (Queen Katia). Anairis Quinones (Karina). Isabella Russo (Sena). Jermaine Fowler (Royal Attendant). Antonio Raul Corbo (Felipe). Jordan Preston Carter (Kiwi Boy). Mixie Chen (Ara)

Language English.

Producers Elise Allen. Drew Barrymore. Matthew Berkowitz. Kristin Cummin/Epgs. Savannah Guthrie. Nancy Juvonen. Heather Renney. Ember Truesdell. Jennifer Twiner McCarron. Series Casting By. Allyson Bosch. Series Art Direction by. Jennifer Llewellyn.

Production Atomic Cartoons. Flower Films (II). Netflix Studios.

No. of Seasons 1

No. of Episodes 14

Status OnGoing (2023–)
